Tomb Raider: The Last Revelation (NTSC-U) *Repack*
--------------------------------------------------
Ripped: Nothing.
Downsampled: Videos.
Source: GD dump.

I repacked this game because I made my first release long time ago, when I didn't have so much
experience working on Dreamcast as I have now. Improvements are present in video, that has
untouched audio and video downsampled using VBR, so quality loss didn't got that big. Additionally,
I have optimized file order better than last time, so loading times and reader's movement must be
better. Enjoy.

Features of my release:
- Not corrupted files at all, it was made with GD dump files.
- Used custom file order based on GD's. It means faster loadings and less Dreamcast reader noise.
- Selfboot.

About the game:
- It has VGA Box support.

Other comments:
- "Extras" folder in the pack contains some useless stuff.
- Release comes with manual and covers.